Text: What does WS and DSR stand for?

EarLie: WS=widescreen DSR=Digital Stream Rip. dsr refers to all 480i digital stream rips, the ws denotes its widescreen. it doesn't mean any footage was removed, just that the source was letterboxed and cropping removes the additional filesize of the black bars.

Thank you for the download.

For those interested, it is the CENSORED version.
